NAME
    App::Rad::Plugin::MoreHelp - App::Rad plugin for providing extra help
    info.

VERSION
    version 0.0001

SYNOPSIS
        use App::Rad qw(MoreHelp);

        sub setup {
            my $c = shift;
            $c->more_help('This string gets appended to the main help message.');
        }

        App::Rad->run();

DESCRIPTION
    This is an App::Rad plugin for providing extra help info. It provides a
    "more_help" method which can be used to provide extra info that will be
    appended to to bottom of the help message.

METHODS
  more_help
        $c->more_help('This string gets appended to the help message.');

